  "description": "Voice 1: Wavetable at position 0.08 (nearly sine) with 4x unison. Voice 2: Filtered Noise at color 0.15 (deep oceanic rumble). HAMMER at +0.4 — moderate LOVE blends the tonal and textural. The unison detune at 7.03 cents creates a beating frequency of approximately 1.2 Hz — the tempo of ocean waves at a calm shore. The Drift Anchor trick: voice drift at 0.15 depth. Pelagic: of the open ocean.",
